Package: ojsr
Type: Package
Title: OJS Scraper for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Gaston", "Becerra", email = "gaston.becerra@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows you scrap content (bibliographic metadata) from OJS front-pages and their OAI interfaces; 
    This is useful when the OJS Rest API is not available (as in OJS installments prior to v3.1). 
    It also includes function to parse OJS specific URL conventions. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    oai,
    rvest,
    stringr,
    tidyverse,
    urltools,
    xml2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
